         newsletter
        ============
        
        +------------+----------------------------------------------------------------+
        |**About**   | newsletter is for making newsletters with python.              |
        +            | In *very* early stages of development.                         +
        |            | See COPYING for LGPL licence details.                          |
        +------------+----------------------------------------------------------------+
        |**Authors** | Only one developer so far, maybe more if it becomes useful.    |
